sequenceDiagram
actor LoanApplicationModule
participant InterestPricingModule
participant CreditScoringEngine
LoanApplicationModule->>InterestPricingModule: Request interest rate (customer ID, loan amount)
InterestPricingModule->>CreditScoringEngine: Request credit score (customer ID)
CreditScoringEngine->>InterestPricingModule: Return credit score
InterestPricingModule->>InterestPricingModule: Calculate interest rate based on risk profile
InterestPricingModule->>LoanApplicationModule: Return interest rate